  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "Stdb/hbXkRgGwTJ/Ryfy6t08X4zYVoOzwmlJUITuh70=",
    "originContent": "- **Proof-of-Work Engine:** Replaces visual puzzles with a computational challenge that is easy for users but hard for bots.",
    "translatedContent": "- **工作量证明引擎：** 用计算挑战替代视觉谜题，对用户友好但对机器人难以应对。"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "0n1lGD9yR+iAfIEubVja68FyQGZEJaAWzudKPNPgSs4=",
    "originContent": "- **Stateless & Secure:** Uses signed JSON Web Tokens (JWTs) for challenge/response cycles, eliminating server-side session state.",
    "translatedContent": "- **无状态且安全：** 使用签名的 JSON Web Token (JWT) 进行挑战/响应，消除服务器端会话状态。"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "DorF9QmEgAtPWZTj2+uUYvlIZ/VYM+OiF5hL5s/UBnE=",
    "originContent": "- **Replay Attack Prevention:** Leverages Redis Bloom filters for high-performance, time-windowed prevention of challenge reuse.",
    "translatedContent": "- **防重放攻击：** 利用 Redis Bloom 过滤器实现高性能、基于时间窗口的挑战重用防护。"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "tPB6ubZgsBHYBzbij9sT+e1Dvoojx7UhstxuY+L6A7Y=",
    "originContent": "- **Embeddable Client Widget:** A lightweight, dependency-free JavaScript widget that integrates easily into any web form.",
    "translatedContent": "- **可嵌入客户端组件：** 轻量、无依赖的 JavaScript 组件，轻松集成至任何网页表单。"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "dSD3S82T8fRZxispJ6nSW4GFsXTd6WiNMdFodAvGTIo=",
    "originContent": "- **Configurable:** Easily adjust PoW difficulty, CORS origins, and ports via environment variables.",
    "translatedContent": "- **可配置：** 通过环境变量轻松调整 PoW 难度、CORS 源和端口。"
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "+25g9iH+E9kk+U1zt+BqqZy+ojTobNCBeptttMVI4xE=",
    "originContent": "- **Containerized:** Full Docker and Docker Compose support for easy deployment of the backend server and its Redis dependency.",
    "translatedContent": "- **容器化：** 完整支持 Docker 和 Docker Compose，方便部署后端服务器及其 Redis 依赖。"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "7BdmtcqWr6zj98Xk9lpJYWBw+8crN0+NQcCEGlGCJDM=",
    "originContent": "- **Full-Stack Demo:** Includes a complete Express.js + TypeScript example to demonstrate a real-world integration.",
    "translatedContent": "- **全栈演示：** 包含完整的 Express.js + TypeScript 示例，展示真实世界的集成方式。"
  },
