    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 164,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "| 变量               | 描述                                                                                                                                                                                                  | 默认值               |"
  },
  {
    "row": 165,
    "rowsha": "4RSZe7Uh5ZBmCeNaw2e0toSrVqArwvh8W/5bmwlCr7A=",
    "originContent": "| Variable           | Description                                                                                                                                                                                            | Default              |",
    "translatedContent": "| ------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------- |"
  },
  {
    "row": 166,
    "rowsha": "R3SAMqxvdnler0SxnmGvsANnM4P4/mKJMIQcJFmzaeU=",
    "originContent": "| ------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | -------------------- |",
    "translatedContent": "| `LISTEN_PORT`      | 服务器监听的端口号。                                                                                                                                                                                   | `8080`               |"
  },
  {
    "row": 167,
    "rowsha": "yTbDK+O4To7r3Xz5KqL6uSSMebxGHp9waEFsS6D43O0=",
    "originContent": "| `LISTEN_PORT`      | The port on which the server will listen.                                                                                                                                                              | `8080`               |",
    "translatedContent": "| `REDIS_ADDR`       | Redis 实例的地址。                                                                                                                                                                                     | `127.0.0.1:6379`     |"
  },
  {
    "row": 168,
    "rowsha": "Wl6rN9F2eGiFsXgQSWDJVsoThAO8Czw4d/Ml5N9AzHY=",
    "originContent": "| `REDIS_ADDR`       | The address of the Redis instance.                                                                                                                                                                     | `127.0.0.1:6379`     |",
    "translatedContent": "| `REDIS_DB`         | Redis 数据库编号（0-15）。**注意：** Redis 集群仅支持 DB 0。                                                                                                                                          | `0`                  |"
  },
  {
    "row": 169,
    "rowsha": "XCX0DOWGs2nDGmEBABG4VKnjxnhQVOC2kvrnfgDPGwM=",
    "originContent": "| `REDIS_DB`         | Redis database number (0-15). **Note:** Redis Cluster only supports DB 0.                                                                                                                              | `0`                  |",
    "translatedContent": "| `DIFFICULTY`       | PoW 哈希要求的前导零数量。值越大难度越高。                                                                                                                                                            | `4`                  |"
  },
  {
    "row": 170,
    "rowsha": "1/mPoXWUqH9eDzz0DLXVNf/uuxtkfX7vaXucyP2oibQ=",
    "originContent": "| `DIFFICULTY`       | Number of leading zeros for the PoW hash. Higher is harder.                                                                                                                                            | `4`                  |",
    "translatedContent": "| `ALLOWED_ORIGINS`  | 用逗号分隔的 CORS 允许来源列表（例如，`https://domain.com`）。                                                                                                                                         | `*`                  |"
  },
  {
    "row": 171,
    "rowsha": "CoMOIKfPA5RHCEMqdTJeMLkcVh8ojHirJz5DWlxlYyQ=",
    "originContent": "| `ALLOWED_ORIGINS`  | Comma-separated list of origins for CORS (e.g., `https://domain.com`).                                                                                                                                 | `*`                  |",
    "translatedContent": "| `BASE_PATH`        | 服务器的基础路径。注意：对于非 `/` 路径，客户端使用时应使用 `data-challenge-url`。详见 [这里](https://wicketkeeper.io/components/frontend-widget.html#configuration)。                                   | `/`                  |"
  },
  {
    "row": 172,
    "rowsha": "TZQumw8cI1vJRZ5JAQyWSdfCbkDfc0UW6/BngQ8Bm84=",
    "originContent": "| `BASE_PATH`        | Base path for the server. Note: For paths other than `/` you should use `data-challenge-url` when using the client. See [here](https://wicketkeeper.io/components/frontend-widget.html#configuration). | `/`           |",
    "translatedContent": "| `PRIVATE_KEY_PATH` | 用于存储 Ed25519 私钥的路径。如果不存在则会创建。                                                                                                                                                     | `./wicketkeeper.key` |"
  },
  {
    "row": 173,
    "rowsha": "XBVgDyp2jXYJPIXsLvtY4RTLySCf52UtvT/i2scYK58=",
    "originContent": "| `PRIVATE_KEY_PATH` | Path to store the Ed25519 private key. Will be created if it doesn't exist.                                                                                                                            | `./wicketkeeper.key` |",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
